OL,3,CCatholic priest found guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing child
OL,6,FJersey's Royal Court has found a
OL,7,Fformer Catholic priest guilty on three
OL,8,Fcounts of gross indecency with a child.
OL,10,FPiotr Antoni Glas, 61, committed his
OL,11,Fcrimes on multiple occasions against a
OL,12,Fteenage boy between 2004 and 2007.
OL,14,FThere were cries from the public dock
OL,15,Fwhen the guilty verdicts were read
OL,16,Fout, after an eight-day trial.
