OL,6,F"The victim has shown a tremendous
OL,7,Famount of courage to report this
OL,8,Fabuse, not only to seek justice to
OL,9,Fwhat had happened to them in the past,
OL,10,Fbut also to safeguard others in the
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FThe court had heard how Piotr carried
OL,14,Fout 'exorcisms' on his victim and
OL,15,Fwould 'playfight' with the complainant
OL,16,Fbefore committing sexually motivated
OL,17,Facts.
