OL,6,FA statement from Bishop of Portsmouth
OL,7,FPhilip Egan says: "I wish to express
OL,8,Fmy deep sorrow for the crimes
OL,9,Fcommitted by Fr Glas and to express my
OL,10,Fprofound apologies to the survivor for
OL,11,Fthe abuse they have suffered and the
OL,12,Fpain they have carried over the course
OL,13,Fof their life as a consequence of such
OL,14,Fgrave offences.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts and prayers are with
OL,17,Fthem and their family. The Catholic
OL,18,FDiocese of Portsmouth is committed to
OL,19,Fensuring the safety and protection of
OL,20,Fall those within our parishes and
OL,21,Fchurch communities.
