OL,6,F"There are robust safeguarding
OL,7,Fstandards, policies and procedures in
OL,8,Foperation within the Diocese ` and
OL,9,Findeed throughout the Catholic Church
OL,10,Fin England and Wales.
OL,12,F"We report all allegations of abuse to
OL,13,Fthe relevant statutory authorities,
OL,14,Fand we will continue our commitment to
OL,15,Fprovide safe places for everyone."
OL,17,FPiotr Antoni Glas will be sentenced on
OL,18,FFriday 11 April, and will be remanded
OL,19,Fin custody until that date.
